  "decision_conditions": [
    "The proposed mansard roof extension would be visible from the street, including long views and would constitute an incongruous addition to the existing roofline that is harmful to the visual amenity and the appearance of the front of the building, to the terrace as a whole and to the wider street scene.  Furthermore, the mansard roof would create an awkward junction with the existing valley roof, detrimental to the appearance of the butterfly roofline at the rear.  The development is contrary to policies D1, D4 and D11 of the Islington Unitary Development Plan (2002) and the Urban Design Guide 2006."
